<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨١٣ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6401">‌مُوسَى بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ </a>، نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1620">‌حَمَّادٌ، </a>أَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6702">‌هِشَامُ</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٩٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بْنُ عُرْوَةَ : «أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">‌أَبَاهُ </a>كَانَ يَقْرَأُ فِي صَلَاةِ الْمَغْرِبِ بِنَحْوِ مَا تَقْرَءُونَ: <span class="c3">{وَالْعَادِيَاتِ}</span> وَنَحْوِهَا مِنَ السُّوَرِ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2577">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>: هَذَا يَدُلُّ أَنَّ ذَاكَ مَنْسُوخٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2577">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>: هَذَا أَصَحُّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>